sentences.english: Is no substitute for showing off the core of her unique style.

sentences.english: Mr Dobson also has an unmatched power-base.
sentences.chinese: 杜布森还拥有无可比拟的权力基础。

sentences.english: There was no denying that she had compromised herself irretrievably .
sentences.chinese: 她已经无可挽救地跟他妥协，那是不能否认的了。

sentences.english: There can be no gainsaying of the fact that racial injustice engulfs this community.

sentences.english: Two sentences, admittedly, but what a pair.

sentences.english: He is still, in the eyes of some, an irredeemable misogynist.
sentences.chinese: 在某些人的眼里，他仍然是个无可救药的厌恶女性者。

sentences.english: Unequaled selection of both new and used equipment.

这些都是无可讳言的事实。
